{"tid":2370292,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"諗返起，有冇試過做新人第一日返工唔敢去屙屎？","createTime":"2021-01-18T02:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T04:08:39.000Z","uid":40930,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"661d3fe44e7e4f6c042b5f62b65c797d45ec669d","tid":2370292,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"又到轉工季節<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n令我回想起以前做新人嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多時第一日返工，啲人識你老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上司又驚你未慣未熟唔俾嘢你做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果就自己死埋一邊係到睇資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇睇下有啲急<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔好意思去廁所屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n到而家返咗咁多年工，真係好後悔冇去屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n道理好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">返工冇嘢做咪去屙屎囉</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">返日到個位都冇嘢做咪去第二轉囉</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265b8c3d9e18f836e44a127c45c12e38c325c564","tid":2370292,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />忍到lunch 先敢去屙"},{"pid":"788a5cc7a927ae271854327516739f2f2b376fab","tid":2370292,"uid":40930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"265b8c3d9e18f836e44a1